<item>
 <title>Delays expected</title>
 <link>http://quietlittlelies.com/article/delays-expected</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-type-date field-field-date-published&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;span class=&quot;date-display-single&quot;&gt;26 Jan 2004&lt;/span&gt;        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field-type-text field-field-summary&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;p&gt;How can we thank you enough, good doctor?&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Where do you think you are closing, Dr Beeching?&lt;br /&gt;
Is this how a railway’s run?&lt;br /&gt;
We are the ones who will suffer for your crime&lt;br /&gt;
We are the ones who won’t get to work on time&lt;br /&gt;
So how much of our network’s network are you closing,&lt;br /&gt;
How long till your work is done?&lt;/p&gt;
